# Generate CytoTRACE colors

temp[6] <- "gold"
col <- colorRampPalette(temp)(50)

p <- ggplot(table, aes(x=Component1, y=Component2, color=CytoTRACE)) + 
  geom_point(size=1) + scale_color_gradientn(colours = rev(col)) +
  theme_classic()

DefaultAssay(seurat_obj) <- "Spatial"

# Use UMAP from Monocle3
cds0 <- as.cell_data_set(seurat_obj)

cds0 <- cluster_cells(cds0, reduction_method='UMAP')

# learn graph for pseudotime
cds <- learn_graph(cds0, use_partition = FALSE)

# plot the pseudotime graph:
p1 <- plot_cells(
  cds = cds,
  color_cells_by = "annotation",
  show_trajectory_graph = TRUE, cell_stroke = 0, cell_size = 1,
  label_principal_points = TRUE,
) + scale_color_manual(values = col)

options(repr.plot.width = 6, repr.plot.height = 5)
#pdf('p01.umap_monocle.new.pdf', 5.5, 5)
p1$layers[[1]] <- NULL
print(p1)
#dev.off()
